column1: Historic Data For Illinois River at Marseilles Lock and Dam

column2: River Mile: 244.5 miles above the mouth of the Illinois River

column1: The Marseilles  Lock tailwater gage is located at river mile 244.5.   The Marseilles  Dam is located at river mile 247, immediately upstream from the Marseilles Highway bridge.
This gage is operated by the US Army Corps of Engineers (Rock Island District).
